data.description: Welcome to your new home nestled in the heart of the city! This bright and stylish Capitol Hill 1 bed, 1 Bath condo is the pinnacle of convenient living and boasts nearly 500 sqft of private patio with your own exterior entrance.  2 retractable awnings on the patio make this space a secluded urban oasis with everything a city-dweller could need.   Remodeled in 2023, the gorgeous unit has an open floor plan, new kitchen, new bathroom, new spilt A/C, windows, a brand new exterior door for your private entrance.  Channel your inner chef with the new induction stove, hood, and open floor plan to impress your guests!  Everyone will enjoy spending time on the gorgeous rooftop patio with 360 degree views of the neighborhood and Colorado's incredible sunsets. Trader Joe's or restaurants like  Carboy, Logan Street, Mizuna, Table 6 or Vesper are just outside your door. You'll find Denver staples like Pablo's and Angelo's a few blocks away, as well as a nearby Safeway, hospitals, and so many other incredible restaurants and amenities.  Countless parks, the Denver Art Museum, Library, Arboretum, Capitol Building, and endless destinations are only moments away from this phenomenal, unique home. Easy access to highways and major streets will make your commute a breeze. You'll love showing off your new spot.  Don't let it slip by.
